individual.name: Wakron, Inc. (WRKN)
individual.overview: Wakron, Inc. (WRKN) is a technology company headquartered in California, United States. The company develops products for people to connect and socialize with friends, families, and partners. Wakron’s main product WaKO, a decentralized platform for users to chat in text, video calls, and groups.
